Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.21,0:00:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{this game is from chapter 2}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.14,0:00:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.42,0:00:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.26,0:00:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.63,0:00:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.56,0:00:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. I'll take that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.37,0:00:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Kan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.55,0:00:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.42,0:01:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.14,0:01:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.96,0:01:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.32,0:01:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.20,0:01:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Calling Dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.94,0:01:33.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.00,0:01:35.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.50,0:01:39.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.73,0:01:43.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.37,0:01:47.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.43,0:01:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.21,0:01:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit messing with me! \NTake this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.10,0:01:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.53,0:02:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.07,0:02:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.06,0:02:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up to {muzu}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.00,0:02:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The time is not yours to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.78,0:02:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Shut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.52,0:02:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.83,0:02:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool! A cheap trick like that doesn't deserve to be called cheating!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.86,0:02:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Calling Dragon, I was looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.52,0:02:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,For me? Let go of his hand and maybe I'll hear you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.97,0:02:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:03:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that you hate the yakuza.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.13,0:03:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But being a pro gambler is even worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.76,0:03:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The yakuza don't deceive other yakuza.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.38,0:03:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But for gamblers like you, it's a way of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.09,0:03:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They're lower than dirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.20,0:03:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe once you're in front of the president, you'll learn to stay in line.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.80,0:03:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon, take off your sunglasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And put out your cigarette.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.99,0:03:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you give me the ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.41,0:03:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.44,0:03:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yessir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.38,0:03:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.19,0:03:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta go, little missy. We can play some more once the grown-up talk is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Murota! You came by yourself? Where's your boss, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.73,0:04:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... So his wife's been hospitalized? \NThat's tough for both of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.05,0:04:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But she was taken in by ambulance? \NIn that case it must be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.59,0:04:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess Kawachi's gone soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.78,0:04:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,His wife is more important than a promise between bosses now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.94,0:04:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Shozo! One's wife takes precedence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My apologies... Once my boss is done with the formalities, he'll come here immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.03,0:04:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Murota, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, hurry up and call in Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yessir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.52,0:04:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and greet the president!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.12,0:04:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Cretin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Kneel down and pay your respects!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.96,0:04:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. No need for greetings when we're about to face off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.60,0:04:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what they say - might makes right! Don't they, Calling Dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.38,0:05:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.77,0:05:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That was too quick, Shozo.\NI was about to get a yakuman...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite the joke, president...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.64,0:05:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.14,0:05:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.82,0:05:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:06:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Another quick win, eh, Shozo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.97,0:06:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better watch out. \NNext time I'll get my yakuman!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.82,0:06:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.83,0:06:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.91,0:06:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.87,0:06:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you supposed to be a yakuza? {I copied this dialogue from manga so many times I can now tell it by heart}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.22,0:06:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? What did you just say, young man?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.36,0:06:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it considered shameful for yakuza to deceive others?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.01,0:06:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you take those sunglasses off?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.27,0:06:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the fun and games are over, Shozo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.44,0:06:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I'm losing my knack. To think I'd be caught by a kid,of all people...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.48,0:06:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, not bad, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.03,0:07:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like Murota didn't even notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.07,0:07:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No offense to you, though, Murota.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He was putting his winning tile on top of the wall and switching it out...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.83,0:07:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How about that kid, eh, Shozo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.75,0:07:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I want him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.51,0:07:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,President, it's been so long since I met a guy that I absolutely needed to get my hands on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.20,0:07:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouzou, I'll give him to you.\NRefine his skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.44,0:07:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.60,0:07:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A Calling Dragon, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.81,0:07:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Boss Kai has called for you. Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.36,0:07:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If he needs something, he can come to me himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that, you jackass?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.89,0:07:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Dontcha lay a finger on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.54,0:07:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.87,0:07:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm feeling great today, little missy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.99,0:07:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll play ball with you until you get sick of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.41,0:07:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.10,0:08:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon, guess I've come to you, just as you asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.23,0:08:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. \NI'll hear you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.37,0:08:24.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,At that time, war was threatening to erupt in the east.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.40,0:08:24.10,Sign,,0,0,0,,Gangster Blood Feud {暴力団 血の抗争}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:29.80,Sign,,0,0,0,,Sakurado (Influential Gang) Mobilizes {guess; 桜道会全面\N広域暴力団}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.95,0:08:26.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A member of the Shimazu Syndicate,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.87,0:08:29.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,a part of the Oudou-affiliated Kai Group, was stabbed to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.81,0:08:35.00,Sign,,0,0,0,,Miyoshi Family suspect Morita (22) {美好一家 森田容疑者(22)}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:35.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The assailant was M from the Miyoshi Family, a rival of the Oudou Syndicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.00,0:08:37.80,Sign,,0,0,0,,Gang member Morita brutally murdered on the street! {森田組員路上にて惨殺!の}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.64,0:08:37.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It goes without saying that the Oudou Syndicate
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.86,0:08:40.80,Sign,,0,0,0,,Retaliation by the Sakurado-affiliated Kai Family?! {桜道会系甲斐組の報復}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:41.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,immediately enacted retaliatory measures against the Miyoshi Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.80,0:08:43.80,Sign,,0,0,0,,Miyoshi Family executive Takada (38) \Nshot dead at his mistress's house!!! {美好一家高田幹部(38)\N愛人宅にて射殺!!!}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:45.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The Oudou Syndicate boasts of having forces throughout the entire Kanto area.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.80,0:08:46.75,Sign,,0,0,0,,Murder in broad daylight! \NAssistant to the Miyoshi family's lieutenant Ishii (41) shot dead! {白昼殺人!\N美好一家若頭補佐\N石井(41)射殺！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.66,0:08:49.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It is the most widespread crime syndicate in eastern Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.04,0:09:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what being a yakuza is all about!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.53,0:09:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone hits you, you hit them back - several times harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not here to listen to your bragging. \NStop wasting my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.79,0:09:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I am quite certain that you have it in you - \Nthe thing I'm looking for. That's a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You are mine, Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.43,0:09:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I answer to nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.41,0:09:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not anyone's property.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.72,0:09:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon, I'm carrying the burden of 2000 Oudou and Kai members
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.39,0:09:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,on my back,you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.35,0:09:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.11,0:09:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop making fun of me... \NI need to set a good example for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.60,0:09:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Shozo, how did that dispute with the Miyoshis turn out?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They're as good as dead! If we keep it up, they'll be completely wiped out by next week!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.94,0:10:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's the time, Shozo...\NYou need to pull out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? B-Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.53,0:10:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that the Miyoshis are getting the western syndicates involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.27,0:10:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If the east and west go to war, there'll be no end in sight...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time, Shozo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.36,0:10:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.24,0:10:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! I'm getting off at the next exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.91,0:10:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Boss, this is insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.16,0:10:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be walking out alone right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.32,0:10:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to tell the car in front...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.46,0:10:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care.\NI'm getting off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.55,0:10:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I can win with that one. {from manga}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.97,0:10:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.84,0:11:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.53,0:11:14.49,Thought,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.49,0:11:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.16,0:11:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.46,0:11:25.55,Thought,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.77,0:11:31.54,Thought,,0,0,0,,Who the hell is this guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.63,0:11:40.05,Sign,,0,0,0,,Mahjong
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.94,0:11:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.36,0:11:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? The fuck was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.46,0:11:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A gunshot?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Hey, what'd you just {muzu}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.99,0:12:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.10,0:12:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.87,0:12:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me your luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.48,0:12:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it to the boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.27,0:12:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What was that?! {chapter 5}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.05,0:12:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon went with Miyoshi?! \NWhere? Where the fuck are they going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.48,0:12:45.95,Sign,,0,0,0,,Mahjong Club Peaceful {I have no idea what the character below is so insert any word here; 麻雀クラブ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.73,0:12:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I run a gambling den for the Miyoshi Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.63,0:12:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard the rumors about you, Calling Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently you're a pretty good gambler.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.36,0:13:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But rumors aren't always true!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.56,0:13:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing is believing is what they say. \NYou know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.30,0:13:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's play just one game. I want to get this over with as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.90,0:13:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? {/soon?}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.39,0:13:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.30,0:13:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.90,0:13:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ron.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Urk!\NChinitsu toitoi tanyao...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.90,0:13:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're Miyoshi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the cat was out of the bag from the very start.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.78,0:13:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I saw it and I believe it.\NYou really are an amazing gambler!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.43,0:13:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't take this the wrong way, Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.28,0:14:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It just so happens that this parlor is one of the boss's hideouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.72,0:14:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all there is to it.\NDon't get cocky!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.00,0:14:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting used to the yakuza's idea of entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.02,0:14:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.43,0:14:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably just some punks getting into a fight. {chinpira}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.35,0:14:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody knows that I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.20,0:14:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's resume the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.17,0:14:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Going for suukantsu, eh, Dragon?\NLike that'll ever happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.30,0:14:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.45,0:14:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:15:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Kai! \NYou're supposed to be dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.85,0:15:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, I lived. And indeed, I'm as alive as ever! I'm immortal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.54,0:15:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see, Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.31,0:15:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You know him?! {believing manga TL, maybe he's just trying to be friendly}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.32,0:15:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon, it's all thanks to you that I was able to find Miyoshi here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.57,0:15:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm truly grateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.77,0:15:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need your thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.66,0:15:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You can just call off the dogs that keep following my every step, and we're square.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.96,0:15:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't changed a bit, my boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.13,0:15:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Pardon me butting in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.05,0:15:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to interfere while you're in the middle of a game. Please go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.51,0:15:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe it was your turn?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.40,0:15:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Shithead!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.70,0:15:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Kan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.03,0:15:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon, you're just one step away from suukantsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.76,0:15:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Motherfucker!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.41,0:16:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, it seems it's Miyoshi's turn. Hurry up to draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.26,0:16:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Kan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.52,0:16:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon! Where are you going? The game's not over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.94,0:16:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.49,0:16:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, keep your eyes on Dragon at all times, understand? He is my treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.56,0:16:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't die before I get my hands on that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.06,0:17:01.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The fact that Kai Shouzou of Oudou's Kai Group assassinated Miyoshi himself
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.06,0:17:05.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,sent a shockwave throughout the underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.16,0:17:11.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It showed that the Oudou Syndicate was a force to be reckoned with.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.83,0:17:14.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But more importantly, it was an exclamation
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.00,0:17:18.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,that put Kai Shouzou's and the Kai Group's names on the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.65,0:17:21.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, the Miyoshi Family, which had lost its leader,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.96,0:17:26.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,was on its last legs. \NTheir destruction was inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.20,0:17:32.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Due to Kai's actions, the conflict came to a tentative end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.05,0:17:33.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,However, as time passed,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.48,0:17:38.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,it felt like unsettling noises began to break the silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.01,0:17:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.34,0:17:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think I've seen him. {assuming they're looking for ryuu}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.99,0:17:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He's probably never been here before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.26,0:17:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck if I know. We've not been seeing him lately. No, it's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.11,0:18:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. \NI really know nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.28,0:18:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,When I woke up this morning, he was already gone. That's all I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.43,0:18:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be the one asking you. \NWhere is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.79,0:18:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Will he ever come back to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.04,0:18:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's useless, Dragon! \NYou can't get away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.31,0:18:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you wait, Dragon!\NI'll be seeing you real soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.01,0:18:31.92,Sign,,0,0,0,,Inn {旅荘}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.14,0:18:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no room for mistake. \NIt's the Calling Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.04,0:18:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,One can't forget that irritating face he has!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.26,0:18:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Calling dragon! But why is he playing in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.70,0:18:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.31,0:18:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Did he just riichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.25,0:18:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon declared riichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.30,0:18:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Now that I think about it, \Nhe hasn't called even once yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.49,0:19:16.42,Sign,,0,0,0,,Restroom
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.49,0:19:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Calling Dragon? There's no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.42,0:19:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's he in a gambling den like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.81,0:19:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got no idea either, \Nand it's creeping me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.61,0:19:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And it seems like the Oudou Gangs are always on his tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.74,0:19:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oudou Gangs?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.02,0:19:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up! You absolutely cannot lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.57,0:19:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Underestimating the yakuza is a way to get yourself killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.16,0:19:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? \NYour hands are shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.65,0:19:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Kan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.38,0:19:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.03,0:19:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.22,0:20:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.40,0:20:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.93,0:20:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.18,0:20:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That means I haven't had three meals, not even one, and it's my first or second time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.37,0:20:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.70,0:20:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Calling dragon, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.56,0:20:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you come to this backwater den?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.05,0:20:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not gonna find anything worth your while out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.76,0:20:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Kan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.41,0:20:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I just felt like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.01,0:20:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Calling Dragon, can I ask you one more thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.57,0:20:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Why haven't you called before?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.19,0:20:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If the rumor's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.69,0:20:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Did you say Calling dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.12,0:20:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It can't be true! \NProve it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:20:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.08,0:21:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Kan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like my life grows shorter every time I call.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.63,0:21:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one call should enough against you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.74,0:21:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.30,0:21:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.54,0:21:35.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,On that day, Dragon glided deftly through the silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.61,0:21:42.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It was as if he had abandoned his fate to the flow of time itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.87,0:21:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon, I've been waiting for you to come out. {chapter 7}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.72,0:22:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That was quite a long game. \NDid you have fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.39,0:22:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon, stab me with this. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.42,0:22:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't trying to run away while I was gone, were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.40,0:22:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Now come! Hurry up and stab me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.70,0:22:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't running away from you. \NI just felt like going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.77,0:22:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon, I've had just about enough of playing this cat-and-mouse game with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.40,0:22:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it about time to settle this once and for all?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.40,0:22:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon, have a match with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.99,0:22:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A match to end all matches. \NIf I win, you're mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.54,0:22:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If you win, you can take my life and do whatever you want with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.90,0:22:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon! If you're a man, then put your life on the line and come at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.26,0:22:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Come and put your life on the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.65,0:22:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,"Come and put your life on the line?"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.86,0:23:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Really now, Shozo?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.47,0:23:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you seriously expect him to come here just because of those words?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.31,0:23:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll come. \NI know he will.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.17,0:23:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon's mahjong isn't half-hearted.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.13,0:23:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He's always gambling with his life...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.32,0:23:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's just his bread and butter. \NIt's in his blood, even.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.13,0:23:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He knows that fighting is the only way he can continue to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.98,0:23:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to keep fighting until it finally destroys him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.75,0:23:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that is his destiny. \NThat's just how Dragon is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.23,0:23:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon... \NYou're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.50,0:23:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The passage of time \Nmeans nothing to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.87,0:23:56.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The first round began under the most strange of circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.82,0:23:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.50,0:24:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.40,0:24:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Apologies, that's a pon for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.63,0:24:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Shozo, now you're calling too?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.08,0:24:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure is a strange evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.29,0:24:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.62,0:24:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.85,0:24:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.88,0:24:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.15,0:24:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A battle of pons! How fascinating!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.86,0:24:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Maruko, was it you who taught Shozo this tactic?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.00,0:24:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to catch a tiger, you have to enter its den.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.69,0:24:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like you could've made daisangen, Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.78,0:24:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.35,0:24:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.64,0:24:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like you're out of luck today, Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.49,0:25:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.48,0:25:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.28,0:25:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.64,0:25:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.24,0:25:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, 2,000, 4,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.36,0:25:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon, you're going to lose today.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.62,0:25:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The heavens are on my side!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.07,0:25:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Chun, honitsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.97,0:25:25.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There was no doubt that Kai Shozo had the heavens on his side that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.01,0:25:28.41,Sign,,0,0,0,,Mahjong 841
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.55,0:25:28.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It was as if he was drawing tiles at will.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.84,0:25:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.06,0:25:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Shozo, are you okay? \NYou're sweating a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.12,0:25:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.80,0:25:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I just got a little scratch that's itching...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.18,0:25:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking this pon, Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.29,0:25:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to win this game, Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.33,0:25:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You are already mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.52,0:25:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.25,0:25:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.81,0:25:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is your hand too messed up? {no idea why he asks that, maybe "is your hand tired"}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.38,0:26:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.72,0:26:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.54,0:26:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that chii really a good idea, Dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.38,0:26:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't win unless you get a haneman direct hit or sanbaiman tsumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.31,0:26:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not stealing tiles with my calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.00,0:26:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm imbuing them with life.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.91,0:26:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop meddling in my affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.22,0:26:32.95,Thought,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.58,0:26:37.29,Thought,,0,0,0,,What is Dragon waiting on?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.29,0:26:42.25,Thought,,0,0,0,,Could he have another middle wait? \NThat would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.25,0:26:43.24,Thought,,0,0,0,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.24,0:26:46.80,Thought,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine. I'm in luck today!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.80,0:26:49.21,Thought,,0,0,0,,The heavens are on my side!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.38,0:26:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Shozo!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.41,0:26:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Shozo!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.27,0:26:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Shozo?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.38,0:26:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's all fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.84,0:26:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Please sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.38,0:27:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.08,0:27:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's do or die!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.47,0:27:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.94,0:27:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.93,0:27:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.29,0:27:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Shozo! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.17,0:27:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What a wonderful victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.61,0:27:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it, Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.39,0:27:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You still have one matter to settle, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.92,0:27:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A promise is a promise. \NTake my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.94,0:27:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so fast, Dragon kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.95,0:27:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's a shred of humanity left in you,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.93,0:27:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,how can you leave without even acknowledging Kai's words?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.20,0:28:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My poor daughter... Kai's wife, she didn't tell anyone else, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.83,0:28:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A lead ball was lodged in his lung.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.38,0:28:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It needs to be taken out as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.88,0:28:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,However, he only has a fifty-fifty chance of surviving the operation...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.51,0:28:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet he absolutely refused to undergo the surgery!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.93,0:28:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If only you could see how bitterly she cried as she held onto me...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.11,0:28:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He only has three months left... \NWhat Kai did was...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.01,0:28:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,bet those three months on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.11,0:28:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey pops, don't say a word more.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.74,0:28:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're making me look pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.02,0:28:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Dragon? \NHurry up and take my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.04,0:28:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you carrying the burden of 2,000 people on your back?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.13,0:28:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Cherish that burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.40,0:28:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.93,0:29:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ch-Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.23,0:29:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What did you say? \NChief was shot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.12,0:29:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't anyone protect him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.28,0:29:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Where were his bodyguards?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.97,0:29:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?! Kai was with him? \NWhat the fuck has he been doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.38,0:29:39.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That morning, 36 of the Oudou's upper leaders assembled in secrecy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.97,0:29:43.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The pressing topic, naturally, was the shooting of the Oudou
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.29,0:29:45.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Syndicate president the previous night.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.51,0:29:47.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The meeting was tumultuous from the very start.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.61,0:29:51.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The anti-Kai faction pinned the blame on Kai for the incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.39,0:29:54.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and demanded that he step down from his position.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.92,0:29:59.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kawachi Koichi, the leader of the anti-Kai faction, said:
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.03,0:30:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.56,0:30:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we hold a secret ballot in order to reach a consensus regarding this incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.96,0:30:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, no need for a vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.25,0:30:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm prepared to accept the consequences at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.59,0:30:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,However! I need to give them payback before then. Until I'm finally satisfied...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.85,0:30:23.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With those words from Kai, \Nthe meeting was adjourned.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.23,0:30:31.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,One week later,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.78,0:30:35.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,a man's corpse was discovered on Mount Takao, brutally murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.25,0:30:41.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The corpse was lidentified as S, 36 years old, a member of the Miyoshi Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.51,0:30:45.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It was confirmed that he was the one who shot the Oudou Syndicate president.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.28,0:30:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, I'll be taking that pon.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.48,0:30:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.63,0:30:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Kan.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.63,0:31:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.68,0:31:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.93,0:31:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.05,0:31:13.71,Thought,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.72,0:31:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.72,0:31:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Are you talking to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.38,0:31:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not in this for much longer. {lit: your back is sooty - I don't understand the metaphor, but essentially it's ryuu's way of saying "you've already lost"; https://manba.co.jp/topics/21894}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.40,0:31:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.88,0:31:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, kid, I don't understand what this whole "in this for longer" means.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.28,0:31:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you keep talking shit, you're in for a world of hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.46,0:31:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.38,0:31:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What'd you just say, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.88,0:31:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a ron.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.91,0:31:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.68,0:31:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.21,0:31:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.68,0:31:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.77,0:31:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.62,0:32:06.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The Kai Group,over 2500 members strong, including the low-ranking ones,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.97,0:32:11.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,began a massacre under Kai Shozo's command.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.30,0:32:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up! We're gonna kill every last one of those Miyoshi bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.26,0:32:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.64,0:32:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.10,0:32:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.63,0:32:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.63,0:32:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.68,0:32:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.56,0:32:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! Here we go! I really needed this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.34,0:32:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.92,0:32:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.24,0:32:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.41,0:32:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.53,0:33:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I went this far so that the president
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.23,0:33:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,would become the greatest boss in the whole country!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.36,0:33:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to do, if... \NIf he's gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.35,0:33:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What have i been living for this whole time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.76,0:33:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!\NDon't let him die!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.02,0:33:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd give my own life many times over!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.68,0:33:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't let the old man die now!\NI'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.33,0:33:33.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,For the first time, Dragon felt a certain kinship with Kai's soul. {"felt like he could truly understand Kai" in manga but I think they misunderstood it because later they say that kai lives in ryuu and at this moment kai is dying so I think it's closer to "he felt kai's soul moving into his body"}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.50,0:33:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You, the {muzu}.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.13,0:33:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Earlier, you said that I'm not in this for much longer, isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.83,0:33:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd really appreciate it if you explained what the fuck it meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.26,0:33:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't carry the burden of even a single person on your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.02,0:33:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop pretending to be a yakuza.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.56,0:33:59.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Perhaps the true meaning of this phrase could only be revealed
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.44,0:34:01.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,to those who follow the path of destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.36,0:34:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.32,0:34:10.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It was as if Dragon could now hear Kai's cries clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.29,0:34:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me your luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.41,0:34:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it to the old man, Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.44,0:35:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.11,0:35:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.50,0:35:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.84,0:35:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.23,0:35:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.00,0:35:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.54,0:35:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.59,0:35:18.90,Thought,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.50,0:35:23.15,Thought,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.62,0:35:26.74,Thought,,0,0,0,,That's it... \NThat's gotta be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.74,0:35:29.56,Thought,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.39,0:35:35.75,Thought,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.75,0:35:38.41,Thought,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.03,0:35:44.11,Thought,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.10,0:35:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Withdrawal of Japanese territory ba salesman
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.70,0:36:00.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,From that day on, Kai Shozo lived in Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.48,0:36:08.39,Sign,,0,0,0,,Mutual Aid Hospital {whatever the fuck that means; 共済病院}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.80,0:36:14.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,At the same time, Ishikawa Takashi, the second Kai Group boss,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.68,0:36:17.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,showed up at a hospital somewhere in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.62,0:36:21.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Of course, he was here to visit the Oudou boss Sakurada Michizo,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.18,0:36:25.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,who was admitted to the hospital as a long-term inpatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.59,0:36:28.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But for Ishikawa, it was also part of the plan
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.05,0:36:31.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,for fulfilling an important expectation, pinned on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.68,0:36:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.61,0:36:38.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Namely, that important expectation
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.68,0:36:44.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,had been the last wish of his predecessor Kai Shozo, bequeathed to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.73,0:36:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice work,everyone.\NHow about you let me in?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.88,0:36:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,With all due respect, sir, this room is for Kawachi Family members only.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.24,0:36:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No one is allowed inside without the boss's permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.72,0:36:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really? I didn't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.03,0:37:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Ishikawa, second boss of the Kai Group! Will you still not let me in?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.50,0:37:10.10,Thought,,0,0,0,,Ishikawa, these will probably be my last words, so listen carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.10,0:37:14.26,Thought,,0,0,0,,As long as the Oudou Syndicate exists, the Kai Group will be its wall of iron!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.26,0:37:17.81,Thought,,0,0,0,,The Kai Group is the backbone of the Oudou Syndicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.81,0:37:19.27,Thought,,0,0,0,,Do you get it, Ishikawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.27,0:37:23.34,Thought,,0,0,0,,The Kawachis or any other group cannot be that iron wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.34,0:37:26.56,Thought,,0,0,0,,The Kai Group must be the one to carry the Oudou Syndicate upon its back!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.56,0:37:30.45,Thought,,0,0,0,,The Kai syndicate is the iron wall that protects the boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.89,0:37:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and let me in already!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.70,0:37:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,More aggressive calls, eh, bud?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.21,0:37:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna mess up the flow of tiles if you do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.17,0:37:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go with riichi for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.05,0:38:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! A ron!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.22,0:38:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.32,0:38:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.41,0:38:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.02,0:38:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.50,0:38:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.21,0:38:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.11,0:38:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.54,0:38:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now, it's been a while, Boss Kawachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.96,0:38:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been getting pretty full of yourself these days, Ishikawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.17,0:38:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The president's room is Kawachi territory!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.14,0:38:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's off limits to the likes of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.49,0:38:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get straight to the point, if I may.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.86,0:39:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told by the missus herself to come visit the president today!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.81,0:39:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam Sakurada told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.46,0:39:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, fine. Have a seat, Ishikawa.\NOr should I say "new Kai boss?"
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.71,0:39:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You've received quite the promotion!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.30,0:39:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,now listen up,greenhorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.73,0:39:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what Madam Sakurada told you, but the only ones who can see the president
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.80,0:39:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,are his closest officials.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.68,0:39:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess that can't be helped. It was decided at the executive meeting, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.80,0:39:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You never received the cup of sake directly from the boss either.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.78,0:39:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, in the Yakuza world,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.57,0:39:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you can only be admitted into the family by receiving a cup from your superior.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.07,0:39:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't take it personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.08,0:39:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Get it, Ishikawa? You'll just have to work your way up as the new Kai boss, bit by bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.52,0:39:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.26,0:39:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand, but I'm not backing down!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.59,0:39:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I came here today in order to share sake with boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.63,0:40:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Until I share a drink with him, i won't move a single step from this spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.95,0:40:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Ishikawa, what the...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.83,0:40:09.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Later, Kawachi's close associates revealed that at that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.14,0:40:13.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ishikawa stood before Kawachi's, looking as fierce as the yaksha tattooed on his back!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.09,0:40:23.70,Thought,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.23,0:40:26.58,Thought,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.58,0:40:29.61,Thought,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.61,0:40:32.78,Thought,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.53,0:40:43.52,Thought,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.52,0:40:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.31,0:40:49.10,Thought,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.10,0:40:50.96,Thought,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.88,0:40:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Kan!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.50,0:40:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.72,0:41:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.03,0:41:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.77,0:41:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.92,0:41:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.33,0:41:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be winning in mahjong any time soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.10,0:41:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that, you little shit?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.80,0:41:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.53,0:41:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.57,0:41:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.46,0:41:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.35,0:41:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.20,0:41:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.20,0:41:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.07,0:41:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.28,0:41:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.62,0:41:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But man, can you believe this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.25,0:42:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.22,0:42:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Calling Dragon himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.95,0:42:11.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In a gamble, losing means death.\NContinuing to win is life.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.36,0:42:13.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It was Kai Shozo himself who once said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.48,0:42:19.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And now, Dragon once again renewed his search for life-or-death gambles.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.20,0:42:22.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In the end, it truly was just in his blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.44,0:42:25.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It was his destiny and he couldn't change it in a thousand years.
